  1. GI chart code definition

Age of audit tasks

A bar graph calculating whether an audit task is opened and the age of the audit task, showing a visualization of the ages.

  • Report category: Audit activity

  • Required report headers:

    • Primary category: Entry title
    • Secondary category: Comment
    • Tertiary category: Min (Date updated (local time))
    • Primary value: Count

GI chart code definition

    {
    "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v5.json",
    "description": "Stacked bar chart",
    "data": {
        "name": "chartData"
    },
    "transform": [
        {
            "calculate": "if(indexof(datum['$secondary_category'], 'COMPLETE') != -1, 'COMPLETE', 'OPENED')",
            "as": "status"
        },
        {
            "pivot": "status",
            "groupby": [
                "$primary_category",
                "$tertiary_category"
            ],
            "value": "$primary_measure"
        },
        {
            "filter": "!datum.COMPLETE"
        },
        {
            "calculate": "floor((now() - toDate(datum['$tertiary_category'])) / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))",
            "as": "age_days"
        }
    ],
    "width": "container",
    "height": "container",
    "mark": "bar",
    "encoding": {
        "x": {
            "bin": true,
            "field": "age_days",
            "title": "Age of tasks (days)"
        },
        "color": {
            "field": "age_days",
            "type": "quantitative",
            "scale": {
                "scheme": "redyellowgreen",
                "domain": [
                    140,
                    60,
                    0
                ]
            },
            "legend": false
        },
        "y": {
            "aggregate": "count",
            "title": "Number of open tasks"
        }
    }
}
